{"tid":1428733,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急\b]請軍師提早正視 九月開學 會少左人既問題","createTime":"2019-08-07T10:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T10:56:48.000Z","uid":38203,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"deff44d86dc23db787d4e71b39f5ba6f843e9ba7","tid":1428733,"uid":38203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:49:46.000Z","msg":"毫無疑問 依場運動係由一班學生，後生作為主力<br />\n面對九月開學淨返一個月<br />\n大學生可以走堂去繼續支援運動<br />\n但中學生？ 佢地都係今次主力<br />\n我都相信依幾個星期應該會有中學開始做野<br />\n強迫學生要返學，退學會有處罰之類<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n軍師出招<br />\n<br />\n如果罷學，要提早做定宣傳"},{"pid":"db9c2c7a2cd62b626ad7e0b52662fa9a38fe5da8","tid":1428733,"uid":38203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:50:25.000Z","msg":"*逃學會有處罰之類"},{"pid":"710d861f4c705c8a7a42efc8dc241620ecc6b981","tid":1428733,"uid":38203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:51:29.000Z","msg":"根據雨傘既罷學<br />\n其實都有預早計劃，令到教協可以配合，安排<br />\n<br />\n軍師，意見缺一不可"},{"pid":"a306c46371ed3eed0e8ea4e1f82df3e6c80e0a78","tid":1428733,"uid":38203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dfa574e2cd271312e88a5209b416ead344cdb43","tid":1428733,"uid":102185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:54:29.000Z","msg":"開sem一有hall住係出面留幾耐都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29970b6a69cd8f0a10d779740b9eeffbef605d14","tid":1428733,"uid":38203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dfa574e2cd271312e88a5209b416ead344cdb43","tid":1428733,"uid":102185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:54:29.000Z","msg":"開sem一有hall住係出面留幾耐都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:56:48.000Z","msg":"大學唔洗有hall都走堂出到黎啦<br />\n講緊係中學<br />\n唔好唔記得 今次真係唔少00後，中學生站出黎<br />\n最細個被捕人士係13歲呀<br />\n<br />\n班狗都會安排點樣比前線防暴狗休息，尋日擺明換左班新仔\b出黎頂更<br />\n所以真係要正視點樣去罷學"}]}